metadata.name: Love Should Not Hurt #1
metadata.description: The Love Should Not Hurt NFT collection is a series of fan created artwork based on the TEM produced music video Love Should Not Hurt starring Mel B. Owners will have access to exclusive TEM special private events, exclusive concerts by TEM artists, and will gain coveted spots on whitelists for future TEM NFT releases. Further special privileges are available to holders of complete sets of 10 images within the collection.
